title: Wessington
description: Two walks, 7m & 5m, followed by lunch at the Horse & Jockey, Brackenfield Lane, Wessington (just off A615 Matlock Road).  Cost depends on food chosen, wide range available but must order in advance.  Even if you can't walk, please join us for the lunch.  Numbers limited, contact Tony or Sue, 01332 679584.
